description: Bambuser AB engages in the provision of live video streaming service. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 15 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2017-05-05. The company offers a platform IRIS for interactive mobile live video broadcasting and enables the users to stream live video directly from a mobile phone or webcam to the Internet. The IRIS platform comprises two products: IRIS Flow and IRIS Dev. The IRIS Flow is a product suite, which comprises various tools for live video broadcasting, such as access to a browser, a so-called Content Management System (CMS) that includes communication capabilities with the sender (voice/text), filtering capabilities, application program interfaces for integration, among others. The IRIS Dev is a software development kit, which enables integration of live streaming into various iOS and Android applications. The platform allows sharing to the global social networks and is available as a free service for consumers and no-profits, as well as a service for commercial use.
